{"id":"221a1123-e7f6-45c4-8646-512453a02fac","name":"Dominic","description":"<p><strong>“</strong>𝐀𝐟𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐞 𝐲𝐞𝐚𝐫𝐬, 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐛𝐨𝐭𝐡 𝐦𝐞𝐞𝐭 𝐚𝐠𝐚𝐢𝐧</p><p><span style=\"color: #B9B9B9\">Who would've thought that after years of hardship, he would finally have live a good life in peace with his mom. But even though with all the good things that's happening around him, he can't help but feel like there's still a void in his life.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #B9B9B9\">And seeing you after nine years, maybe he finally knows the answer that will fill that void.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 164, 164)\">This bot is suggested by @ellawho. I honestly think she could have made it herself because of the effort in her writing his backstory and all, but nonetheless, I'm glad to have brought her Dominic to life through this bot.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hpwya7J.png\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/39ff8b88-8a48-4c95-9f77-c6a9fe2dc35a_419ebfe5-7674-434b-9de3-b5d1aef0fff2.webp?width=1000\">murder, mentions of abuse, trauma, domestic violence, alcoholism, gambling, bullying, sexual assault, violence against women. !18-year-old user, 19-year-old char.<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/0eBCSl20ixvxmxcY0XwGxj?si=EOVrftZWQweXH8mTwz8HkQ&amp;pi=mQLnCIHKRYWH5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/39ff8b88-8a48-4c95-9f77-c6a9fe2dc35a_f87cf74a-2b46-4cf4-951f-0332a4133160.webp?width=1000\"></a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/39ff8b88-8a48-4c95-9f77-c6a9fe2dc35a_3a2f18f8-f313-4dd9-8fdf-cd376af4ed28.webp?width=1000\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 187, 1